'''蓋爾撞擊坑'''（{{lang-en|Gale}}）是[[火星|火星]]上鄰近[[埃律西昂平原|埃律西昂平原]]的低地邊緣，座標{{coord|5.4|S|137.8|E|globe:Mars}}的大撞擊坑<ref name = usgs/>。它的直徑154公里<ref name="nasanews">[http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/news/msl20110722.html NASA - NASA's Next Mars Rover to Land at Gale Crater]</ref>，並且已經存在了約35至38億年之久<ref name="themis">[http://themis.asu.edu/features/galecrater Mars Odyssey Mission THEMIS: Feature Image: Gale Crater's History Book]</ref>。這個坑的名字來自澳洲天文學家[[華特·弗雷德里克·蓋爾|華特·弗雷德里克·蓋爾]]（Walter Frederick Gale），他於19世紀後期觀測火星，並且描述火星存在著[[火星運河|溝紋]]<ref>[http://adb.anu.edu.au/biography/gale-walter-frederick-6269 Biography - Walter Frederick Gale - Australian Dictionary of Biography]</ref>。

蓋爾坑曾是[[勇氣號火星探測器|勇氣號火星探測器]]的登陸候選地點，現在是2011年11月26日發射，並于2012年8月6日登陸的[[火星科學實驗室|火星科學實驗室]][[好奇號|好奇號]]<ref>[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Curiosity_(rover)]</ref>的登陸地點。

== 地型特徵 ==

蓋爾坑的外貌有著不尋常的特徵，有著大量的碎石環繞著高聳在中心的[[夏普山_(火星)|夏普山]]<ref name="NASA-20120327">{{cite web |author=NASA Staff|title='Mount Sharp' on Mars Compared to Three Big Mountains on Earth|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/multimedia/pia15292-Fig2.html|date=27 March 2012 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=31 March 2012}}</ref><ref name="NASA-20120328">{{cite web |last=Agle |first=D. C.|title='Mount Sharp' On Mars Links Geology's Past and Future|url=http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/msl/news/msl20120328.html|date=28 March 2012 |publisher=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=31 March 2012}}</ref><ref name="Space-20120329">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=NASA's New Mars Rover Will Explore Towering 'Mount Sharp' |url=http://www.space.com/15097-mars-mountain-sharp-curiosity-rover.html |date=29 March 2012 |publisher=Space.com |accessdate=30 March 2012 }}</ref>，這座山比火山口北側的底部高5.5公里，比南側高4.5公里－ 火山口本身的北側也比南側略高。山丘是由成層狀的物質組成，可能是在大約20億年前坍塌的<ref name="themis"/>。這座山丘的起源還不清楚，但是研究顯示它最初可能沉積在湖底，曾經完全充滿著沉積岩，如今只剩侵蝕的殘餘物<ref name="themis"/>。然而，這些結果都還在爭議中<ref>Cabrol et al.  1999.  Hydrogeologic evolution of Gale Crater and its relevance in the exobiological exploration of Mars.  Icarus: 139.  235-245.</ref><ref>Irwin et al.  2005.  An intense terminal epoch of widespread fluvial activity on early Mars: 2. Increased runoff and palelake development.  Journal of Geographical Research:  110. E12S15</ref>。觀測表明上層跨層狀的地形可能是[[风蚀|风积作用]]造成的，但較低層的成因仍然不明確<ref>Anderson and Bell, Geologic mapping and characterization of Gale Crater and implications for its potential as a Mars Science Laboratory landing site, Mars 5, 76-128, 2010, [http://www.marsjournal.org/contents/2010/0004/ doi:10.1555/mars.2010.0004] </ref>。

蓋爾撞擊坑的位置在火星的5.4S, 137.7E<ref name=gmgale>[http://www.google.com/mars/#lat=-3.030812&lon=138.383789&zoom=5&q=gale%20crater Google Mars: Gale crater]</ref>，[[勇氣號火星探測器|勇氣號火星探測器]]（MER-A）的位置在14.57S, 175.47E<ref name=gms/>，[[維京2號|維京2號]]登陸艇在47.93N, 133.74E<ref name=gms>[http://www.google.com/mars/#lat=-5.528510&lon=141.943359&zoom=4&q=spacecraft Google Mars: spacecraft]</reF>。

== 太空船的探測 ==

許多侵蝕進山丘的河道給了科學家們研究地層的好機會<ref name="themis"/>，蓋爾已獲選為[[火星科學實驗室|火星科學實驗室]]的主登陸場<ref>{{cite news|author=The Associated Press|title=NASA Launches Sophisticated Rover on Journey to Mars|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/11/27/science/space/nasas-curiosity-rover-sets-off-for-mars-mission.html|date=2011-11-26|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2011-11-26}}</ref>，它於2011年11月26日發射，2012年8月6日登陸於火星的蓋爾撞擊坑<ref name="launch date announcement">{{cite web|title=Geometry Drives Selection Date for 2011 Mars Launch|url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.cfm?release=2010-171|work=News and Features|publisher=NASA/JPL-Caltech}}</ref><ref name="Gale Crater">{{cite web |last1=Webster |first1=Guy |last2=Brown |first2=Dwayne |title=NASA's Next Mars Rover To Land At Gale Crater |date=2011-07-22 |publisher=[[喷气推进实验室|NASA JPL]] |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.cfm?release=2011-222#1 |accessdate=2011-07-22}}</ref><ref name="Gale Crater2">{{cite web |last1= Chow |first1=Denise|title=NASA's Next Mars Rover to Land at Huge Gale Crater|url=http://www.space.com/12394-nasa-mars-rover-landing-site-unveiled.html |date=2011-07-22|publisher=Space.com |accessdate=2011-07-22 }}</ref><ref name="Gale Crater3">{{cite news |first=Jonathan |last=Amos |title=Mars rover aims for deep crater |date=2011-07-22|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-14249524|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |accessdate=2011-07-22}}</ref>。蓋爾之前曾是2003年的[[勇氣號火星探測器|勇氣號火星探測器]]的登陸候選地點，也是[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]的[[ExoMars|ExoMars]]四個登陸候選地點之一<ref>{{cite web| url= http://article.wn.com/view/2011/05/16/Mars_landing_sites_down_to_final_four/ |title= Mars landing sites down to final four | publisher= [[世界新闻网络|World News (WN) Network]] }}</ref>。

